      • AmenityReader

        public AmenityReader(String file,
                     CoordinateTransformation ct,
                     Map<String,String> osmToMatsimTypeMap)
        Constructing an amenity reader to parse the OpenStreetMap amenities.
        Parameters:
        file - the path to the *.osm OpenStreetMap file;
        ct - the (projected) coordinate reference system to which the WGS84 coordinates of OpenStreetMap will be converted to; and
        osmToMatsimTypeMap - a mapping of OpenStreetMap Amenity values to MATSim activity types.
